23:25.273 --> 23:26.709
THAT WAS NO ACCIDENT.

23:26.840 --> 23:28.450
I BEG YOUR PARDON?

23:28.581 --> 23:29.669
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

23:29.799 --> 23:31.584
WE'VE NEVER HAD PROBLEMS
WITH THE BRAKES

23:31.714 --> 23:32.759
ON OUR TRUCKS BEFORE.

23:35.065 --> 23:37.198
ARE YOU SUGGESTING THAT SOMEONE
TAMPERED WITH YOUR BRAKES?

23:37.328 --> 23:38.199
OH.

23:40.897 --> 23:43.160
AND WHO MIGHT THAT SOMEONE BE?
AS IF I HAD TO GUESS.

23:43.291 --> 23:44.988
HE WAS WASHING MY TRUCK
WHEN I LEFT.

23:45.119 --> 23:46.860
THEREFORE HE'S GUILTY
OF ATTEMPTED MURDER?

23:46.990 --> 23:48.122
COME ON, MITCH,

23:48.252 --> 23:49.602
THAT'S A STRETCH,
AND YOU KNOW IT.

23:49.732 --> 23:51.168
WHAT ABOUT THE SNAKE? HUH?

23:51.299 --> 23:53.170
JUST A COINCIDENCE THE SNAKE
WAS IN MY LOCKER?

23:53.301 --> 23:55.303
AND WHO SAYS
IT WASN'T POISONOUS?

23:55.434 --> 23:56.870
SURE AS HELL
LOOKED POISONOUS TO ME.

23:58.524 --> 24:00.177
HI, MATE.

24:03.616 --> 24:05.008
HEARD YOU HAD A BIT OF BAD LUCK.

24:06.706 --> 24:08.534
JUST WANTED TO MAKE SURE
YOU'RE STILL IN ONE PIECE.

24:12.146 --> 24:14.191
THANKS, WILEY.
IT'S NICE TO KNOW YOU CARE.

24:15.018 --> 24:15.889
RIGHT-OH.

24:17.064 --> 24:18.979
LOOK,
IF THERE'S ANYTHING I CAN DO,

24:19.109 --> 24:20.720
DON'T HESITATE.

24:24.071 --> 24:25.986
WELL,
I GUESS I'LL CALL IT A DAY, EH?

24:27.378 --> 24:28.249
CHEERS.

24:45.092 --> 24:48.182
-GOOD NIGHT, DAD.
-MM. NIGHT, HOBESTER.

24:49.357 --> 24:52.229
YOU, UH, YOU WANT ME
TO GET YOU ANOTHER ICE PACK?

24:52.360 --> 24:54.362
NO. NO, THANKS, PAL. I'M FINE.

24:57.191 --> 24:59.062
YOU, UH, YOU HAD A LONG DAY.

24:59.193 --> 25:00.499
YOU OUGHT TO GET SOME REST.

25:01.238 --> 25:03.632
I'LL BE UP IN A FEW MINUTES.
THANK YOU.

25:04.459 --> 25:05.895
DID I TELL YOU
KAY MORGAN CALLED?

25:07.506 --> 25:08.724
YEAH, YOU DID.

25:09.246 --> 25:10.073
DID YOU CALL HER BACK?

25:11.422 --> 25:12.946
YEAH. I DID CALL HER BACK.

25:13.076 --> 25:14.338
SHE WASN'T HOME.

25:14.904 --> 25:17.080
SHE SAID SHE WANTED TO COME OVER
FOR DINNER SOMETIME.

25:17.777 --> 25:19.126
WHAT SHOULD I MAKE?

25:21.084 --> 25:23.260
WHY DON'T WE TALK ABOUT
THE MENU IN THE MORNING, HUH?

25:24.305 --> 25:25.567
I JUST WANT TO IMPRESS HER, DAD.

25:26.350 --> 25:27.221
YOU SHOULD, TOO.

25:30.659 --> 25:31.965
SHE ONE OF YOUR FAVORITES, HUH?

25:32.792 --> 25:34.141
I DON'T KNOW,
IT JUST SEEMS LIKE...

25:34.271 --> 25:36.186
OUT OF ALL THE WOMEN
YOU'VE EVER DATED,

25:36.796 --> 25:40.147
SHE'S THE ONLY ONE I COULD
REALLY SEE MYSELF CALLING MOM.

25:41.844 --> 25:43.411
THAT'S REAL SWEET, PAL.

25:44.368 --> 25:46.588
I SEE HOW YOU COULD FEEL
THAT WAY.

25:47.763 --> 25:49.722
BUT LET'S NOT RUSH IT. I THINK--

25:49.852 --> 25:51.332
I THINK WE SHOULD AT LEAST

25:51.462 --> 25:53.943
INVITE HER OVER FOR DINNER
BEFORE YOU PROPOSE.

25:54.074 --> 25:55.423
[CHUCKLES]

25:55.554 --> 25:56.555
GOOD NIGHT.

25:57.251 --> 25:58.165
I LOVE YOU, DAD.

25:58.295 --> 25:59.645
I LOVE YOU, TOO, PAL.

26:06.390 --> 26:07.348
NIGHT, DAD.

26:08.392 --> 26:09.437
LOVE YOU, PAL.

26:58.834 --> 27:00.619
