♪ YOU STILL HAUNT ME

29:15.884 --> 29:17.277
MITCH!

29:19.235 --> 29:22.238
-HI.
-HI. ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

29:23.022 --> 29:26.503
YEAH. YEAH. I'M OKAY.
I'M A LITTLE SORE, THAT'S ALL.

29:26.634 --> 29:28.897
YEAH, WILEY TOLD ME
ABOUT THE ACCIDENT.

29:29.028 --> 29:31.291
YEAH. ALLEGED ACCIDENT.

29:32.248 --> 29:33.467
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY ALLEGED?

29:35.469 --> 29:37.384
YOU'VE GOTTEN TO KNOW THIS GUY
PRETTY WELL, HAVEN'T YOU?

29:38.385 --> 29:40.082
NO, I HAVEN'T AT ALL.

29:40.213 --> 29:41.736
COME ON, YOU'VE BEEN SPENDING
A LOT OF TIME WITH HIM.

29:42.781 --> 29:45.479
YEAH, I'VE BEEN LISTENING
TO THIS GUY RATTLE ON.

29:46.088 --> 29:48.569
I MEAN, EVERY TIME I START
TO ASK HIM A PERSONAL QUESTION,

29:48.699 --> 29:52.791
HE, LIKE, LAUNCHES INTO ONE
OF HIS LEGENDARY STORIES.

29:54.749 --> 29:56.359
HE SAY ANYTHING ABOUT ME?

29:57.186 --> 29:58.231
ANYTHING UNUSUAL?

30:01.277 --> 30:02.278
HE ASK ABOUT US?

30:04.063 --> 30:05.107
YEAH.

30:05.238 --> 30:06.500
WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM?

30:07.936 --> 30:09.851
I JUST TOLD HIM
THAT WE WERE FRIENDS.

30:09.982 --> 30:11.200
THAT WAS IT?

30:11.853 --> 30:13.376
THAT WAS IT, MITCH.

30:13.942 --> 30:15.639
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT?
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

30:18.468 --> 30:19.382
I'M NOT SURE YET.

30:26.259 --> 30:27.129
MITCH.

30:29.784 --> 30:30.654
WHAT'S UP, MATT?

30:30.785 --> 30:32.047
GARNER JUST CALLED.

30:32.613 --> 30:34.833
THE POLICE FOUND A PINHOLE LEAK
IN YOUR BRAKE LINE.

30:34.963 --> 30:35.790
THEY SAID
IT COULD HAVE BEEN CAUSED

30:35.921 --> 30:36.835
BY A NAIL ON THE ROAD,

30:37.444 --> 30:38.227
OR...

30:38.358 --> 30:39.750
OR WHAT?

30:39.881 --> 30:41.491
OR IT COULD HAVE BEEN
DELIBERATELY PUNCTURED.

30:41.622 --> 30:43.667
THAT'S IT, COME ON,
GIVE ME YOUR TRUCK.

30:43.798 --> 30:45.321
THEY WON'T KNOW FOR SURE

30:45.452 --> 30:47.062
UNTIL THE RESULTS ARE BACK
FROM THE CRIME LAB.

30:49.586 --> 30:50.457
WHAT TOWER IS WILEY AT?

30:50.587 --> 30:51.893
SWITCHED WITH NEWMIE.

30:52.024 --> 30:53.416
HE SHOULD BE DOWN
AT PARADISE COVE.

30:54.156 --> 30:55.636
MITCH, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

30:56.202 --> 30:57.725
TO GET A FEW THINGS STRAIGHT
WITH WILEY.

31:10.607 --> 31:12.392
KNOCK, KNOCK. HI, STEPH.

31:12.522 --> 31:15.134
HI. THIS JUST CAME FOR YOU
OVER THE FAX MACHINE.

31:15.264 --> 31:16.135
OH, THANKS.

31:18.137 --> 31:20.052
OH, GREAT! ALL RIGHT!

31:20.182 --> 31:21.227
WHAT IS IT?

31:21.792 --> 31:24.099
THIS IS WILEY'S PERSONNEL FILE.

31:24.230 --> 31:26.885
HE GAVE ME
SO MANY DIFFERENT VERSIONS

31:27.015 --> 31:28.538
OF HIS LIFE STORY THAT I KNEW
I HAD TO GET THE FACTS.

31:29.191 --> 31:31.280
LET'S GO LOOK AT IT, HUH?

31:33.543 --> 31:36.024
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

32:24.029 --> 32:24.899
WILEY.

32:26.814 --> 32:27.684
WILEY!

32:41.785 --> 32:43.352
[LINE RINGING]

32:45.964 --> 32:47.139
AH!

32:49.228 --> 32:50.272
AH!

33:08.899 --> 33:11.032
THESE ARE JUST
HIS VITAL STATISTICS.

33:11.946 --> 33:13.339
ISN'T THERE
A PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILE?

33:14.209 --> 33:15.515
I COULDN'T FIND ONE.

33:16.995 --> 33:18.431
OH, BUT HERE'S
SOMETHING INTERESTING.

33:19.388 --> 33:21.825
WILEY TOLD ME THAT HE WAS
A LIFELONG BACHELOR, RIGHT?

33:22.391 --> 33:24.698
BUT ACCORDING
TO HIS FAMILY HISTORY,

33:24.828 --> 33:26.743
HE HAD A WIFE WHO DIED

33:26.874 --> 33:29.137
TWO YEARS BEFORE
HE BECAME A LIFEGUARD.

33:29.268 --> 33:31.096
IT SAYS THAT SHE DROWNED
OFF BONDI BEACH

33:31.226 --> 33:32.575
IN A WINDSURFING ACCIDENT.

33:32.706 --> 33:33.620
BONDI BEACH?

33:33.750 --> 33:35.230
THAT'S WHAT IT SAYS.

33:36.492 --> 33:37.711
DOES IT GIVE HER NAME?

33:38.233 --> 33:40.192
YEAH, BUT I GUESS SHE DIDN'T
CHANGE HER NAME

33:40.322 --> 33:42.455
AFTER THEY GOT MARRIED.
IT'S SHEILA GOLD.

33:43.760 --> 33:44.718
SHEILA GOLD...

33:47.112 --> 33:48.287
OH, MY GOD.

34:15.835 --> 34:18.012
[PANICKED CHATTERING]

34:19.795 --> 34:21.188
WILEY'S LINE IS DEAD.

34:21.320 --> 34:23.409
I TRIED MITCH'S TRUCK.
HE'S NOT ANSWERING.

34:24.409 --> 34:25.454
COME ON.

34:32.286 --> 34:33.984
[CHUCKLES]

34:36.291 --> 34:38.119
[WHISTLES A TUNE]

34:44.473 --> 34:45.779
YOU'VE LED A CHARMED LIFE, MATE.

34:47.607 --> 34:50.088
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU MANAGED
TO SLIP THROUGH MY FINGERS,

34:50.217 --> 34:52.699
BUT I'M NOT TAKING ANY CHANCES
THIS TIME, AM I?

34:59.967 --> 35:01.186
[INHALES]

35:01.969 --> 35:04.537
OOH, I LOVE THE SMELL OF PETROL.

35:04.667 --> 35:05.842
DON'T YOU?

35:06.974 --> 35:08.802
MY WIFE USED TO HATE THE SMELL.

35:09.324 --> 35:10.891
SAID IT MADE HER NERVOUS.

35:11.935 --> 35:13.023
I WONDER WHY.

35:16.114 --> 35:17.898
FUNNY WHAT YOU REMEMBER
ABOUT PEOPLE, EH?

35:19.204 --> 35:21.597
BUT THEN YOU DON'T REMEMBER
MY WIFE, DO YOU?

35:23.512 --> 35:25.862
SHE DIED ABOUT TEN YEARS AGO
AT BONDI BEACH...

35:28.865 --> 35:30.606
WHEN SOME COCKY,
YOUNG YANK LIFESAVER

35:30.737 --> 35:32.173
TRIED TO BE A BLOODY HERO!

35:35.437 --> 35:38.353
IT SAYS RIGHT HERE
IN YOUR TRAINING MANUAL:

35:38.658 --> 35:40.181
"ALWAYS POSITION THE VICTIM

35:40.312 --> 35:41.835
BETWEEN YOURSELF
AND THE PILING."

35:42.836 --> 35:45.143
ALL YOU HAD TO DO
WAS FOLLOW THE RULES, MATE.

35:45.752 --> 35:47.580
I TRIED TO...

35:47.710 --> 35:49.408
WHAT'S THAT? UH?

35:49.538 --> 35:50.887
I TRIED TO...

35:51.018 --> 35:52.062
SHUT UP!

35:52.933 --> 35:54.717
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
YOUR BLOODY ALIBIS.

35:56.241 --> 35:58.895
SHEILA WOULD BE ALIVE TODAY
IF IT WEREN'T FOR YOU.

35:59.635 --> 36:01.942
AND I DON'T CARE
WHAT THE BLOODY DOCTOR SAID!

36:03.726 --> 36:05.075
YOU COULD HAVE SAVED HER, MATE,

36:05.641 --> 36:06.773
BUT YOU DIDN'T.

36:09.863 --> 36:11.821
I'VE WAITED TEN LONG YEARS
FOR THIS MOMENT.

36:13.127 --> 36:14.998
I WISH IT COULD LAST
A LITTLE LONGER,

36:16.957 --> 36:18.785
BUT THEN YOU CAN'T
HAVE EVERYTHING...

36:20.003 --> 36:21.222
CAN YOU?

36:29.709 --> 36:31.145
LIEUTENANT.

36:43.853 --> 36:44.941
CHEERS, MATE.

37:59.929 --> 38:02.889
[SCREAMING, GROANING]

38:08.024 --> 38:09.765
I THINK THAT'S WILEY.

38:14.117 --> 38:15.554
THE TOWER'S ON FIRE!

38:15.684 --> 38:16.990
I'LL CALL IT IN.

38:17.120 --> 38:18.600
KMF-295, WE NEED ASSISTANCE,
PLEASE.

38:43.582 --> 38:45.497
[SCREAMING]

38:54.506 --> 38:55.724
MITCH!

38:56.246 --> 38:57.422
OH, MY GOD, IT'S MITCH.

38:57.552 --> 39:00.163
KMF-295, WE HAVE A BURN VICTIM.

39:15.483 --> 39:17.180
BE CAREFUL, BE CAREFUL, MITCH.

39:17.311 --> 39:18.573
LET ME SEE
HOW BAD YOU'RE BURNED.

39:18.704 --> 39:21.054
I'M OKAY. DID YOU SEE WILEY?

39:21.184 --> 39:22.534
YEAH,
HE WENT OFF ON THAT WAVERUNNER.

39:22.664 --> 39:23.926
GO AFTER HIM.

39:24.057 --> 39:25.493
MITCH,
WE'RE GETTING YOU TO A HOSPITAL.

39:25.624 --> 39:26.973
-I SAID I'M OKAY. GO AFTER HIM!
-NO, MITCH!

39:27.103 --> 39:28.714
-I'M NOT LETTING HIM GET AWAY.
-MITCH!

39:41.727 --> 39:43.772
MITCH, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

39:43.903 --> 39:45.774
COME ON, MITCH, GET HIM.

39:47.428 --> 39:49.169
IT'S PAYBACK TIME!

40:02.095 --> 40:03.488
YES!

40:03.618 --> 40:05.403
YEAH.

40:13.193 --> 40:14.412
EASY, MATE, YOU BLOODY GOT ME.

40:16.457 --> 40:18.067
NICE ROPIN', MITCH.

40:18.198 --> 40:20.243
NOT BAD FOR A BLOODY YANK, HUH?

40:23.333 --> 40:26.249
HOW ABOUT A LITTLE WILEY
ON THE BARBIE TONIGHT, HUH?

41:18.650 --> 41:19.825
PINCH ME.

41:20.478 --> 41:21.348
WHAT?

41:22.001 --> 41:23.959
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
THIS ISN'T A DREAM.

41:24.090 --> 41:25.091
MMM.

41:26.005 --> 41:26.962
MM!

41:27.746 --> 41:29.008
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

41:29.617 --> 41:30.923
YOU SAID, "PINCH ME."

41:31.053 --> 41:32.228
THAT WASN'T A PINCH.

41:32.751 --> 41:34.013
THIS IS A PINCH.

